_sText:
This is a Re-Mix of gg_XBox with some refined textures and serious brushwork to the map to keep it balanced. I saw the rough concept that was being used by XBox and tried to bring it to a top class level. 

This is beta 4 of the map, so I thought I would share with folks outside the [http://fnggaming.net](http://fnggaming.net "http://fnggaming.net") community; The intended style is to be a very fast paced map that people blow through.
